    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You pour evil intent into a skilful slash, which ignores all damage reductions and any hardness the target may have. If the target fails its save, it starts @Condition[bleed]{bleeding} for 1d4+2 rounds, taking 1d6 damage each round until a Treat Injury check (DC 25) is performed, or until it is healed for at least 1 HP by a medical technique. If the used weapon was not of mastercraft quality, it is destroyed beyond repair.</p>\n\n\n\n",
